despoiled"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.: or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"may his camels be affected with the mange,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"scab,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]: it may express a wish that he may be affected with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jarab","text_ar":"جَرَب"},{"kind":"text","text":": or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jariba","text_ar":"جَرِبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"may be put for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ajoraba","text_ar":"اَجْرَبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", to assimilate it to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hariba","text_ar":"حَرِبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": or it may be for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaribato A_ibluhu","text_ar":"جَرِبَتْ اـِبلُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (L.) ―         -b2-  See 4. ―         -b3-  Also (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"halakato A^aroDuhu","text_ar":"هَلَكَتْ اَرْضُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His land had its herbage dried up by drought;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became such as is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jarobaA='","text_ar":"جَرْبَا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":", fem. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ajorabu","text_ar":"اَجْرَبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.]. (K.)"}],"source_refs":["S","A","Mgh","Msb","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n5429","headword_ar":"جِرْبٌ","root":"jrb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jirobapN","text_ar":"جِرْبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n5430","headword_ar":"جَرَبٌ","root":"jrb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mange,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"scab;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a certain disease,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"well known;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, K;) accord. to the medical books, (Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a gross humour, arising beneath the skin, from the mixture of the salt phlegm,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, MF,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the phlegm of the flesh,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(so in a copy of the Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with the blood, accompanied with pustules, and sometimes with emaciation, in consequence of its abundance;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, MF;) or ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an eruption consisting of"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pustules upon the bodies of men and camels."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, TA.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^EodaY mina Aljarabi Einoda AlEarabi","text_ar":"اعْدَى مِنَ الجَرَبِ عِنْدَ العَرَبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"More transitive,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"catching, than the mange,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"scab, among the Arabs"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (A, TA:) a proverb. (TA.) ―         -b2-  (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Rust upon a sword."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b3-  (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A resemblance of rust upon the inner side of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jafon","text_ar":"جَفْن"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"eyelid"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (M, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sometimes covering the whole of it, and sometimes part of it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biA^ajofaAnihi jarabN","text_ar":"بِاَجْفَانِهِ جَرَبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"In his eyelids is"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a resemblance of rust upon their inner sides."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.) ―         -b4-  (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A vice, a fault, a defect, an imperfection,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a blemish."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, K.)"}],"source_refs":["A","Msb","MF","TA","M","K"]},{"entry_id":"n5431","headword_ar":"جَرِبٌ","root":"jrb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ajorabu","text_ar":"اَجْرَبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}